<p>
<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">svasti śrī <supplied reason="undefined"><g type="ddanda">.</g></supplied></hi> kaṉṉara<hi rend="grantha">de</hi><unclear>vaṟ</unclear>ku yāṇṭu <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> Āvatu vāṇakoppāṭit teṉ karai Iraṇa
<lb n="2" break="no"/>pimamaṅkalattu <hi rend="grantha">sabhai</hi>yom nirnila vilaiyāvaṇakkaiyeḻuttu vaṭakarai vāḷai 
<lb n="3" break="no"/>yūrt tāṉṟonṟi Ī<hi rend="grantha">śva</hi>rattu Aiññūṟṟuva vitiviṭaṅkar ttaṇṭi<hi rend="grantha">śva</hi>rariṭai <unclear>p po</unclear>
<lb n="4" break="no"/>ṉ koṇṭu kaṭava poṉ <num value="40">4 <g type="numeral">10</g></num> Oru kaḻañcarai poṉ koṇṭu kaṭavom Ippoṉ
<lb n="5"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> nilamāvatu Eṅkaḷ vāḷaiyūr kaḻaniiṭaip paittulaicceṟuvu<unclear>m</unclear> <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="6"/>ḷḷiṭṭut taṭi Iraṇṭu <unclear>karattu</unclear> Eṭṭu māvum Icceṟuve Aṭaiya teṟki
<lb n="7" break="no"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="7" unit="character"/> kku kiḻpāṟkellaimari <gap reason="lost" quantity="4" unit="character"/> 
</p>

<p>The rest is lost.</p>

